f director Hipia. He recognized Zahai's talent and negotiated his studies at E. Burian. Zahajsky then studied at the DAMU and became a member of the Vinohrady Theater (1961-1965).\n\nIn 1965 Zahajsky became a member of the Theater behind the gate, where he played together with Vladimír Menšík for example in the Maskary of Ostende. In 1972, the Administrative Theater behind the gate was canceled and Zahajský and Libuší Šafránková left for the Činoherní klub. His colleagues included Petr Čepek, Jiřina Třebická, Josef Somr, Jiří Kodet, Jiří Hrzán and others.\n\nJiri Zahajsky made mainly small characters in film and on television. Unforgettable is his character, Inspector Trachta of the comedy Dissolved and launched. He created several roles of criminologists, his beard gave him the opportunity to perform the roles of the grooms, he played in the roles of his fathers (TV series Křeček in the nightgown). Daddy also played in a number of television fairy tales especially in the 1980s.\n\nJiri Zahajsky was for 31 years a life partner of TV advertiser Kamila Moučková, since 1992 she was the fourth husband of actress Jana Brejchová. Jiri Zahajsky died in Prague after a long fight with prostate cancer on July 19, 2007.\n\n(Wikipedia)","name":"Jiří Zahajský","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CZ","iso_639_1":"cs","name":"Český","english_name":"Czech","data":{"biography":"","name":"Jiří Zahajský","primary":true}}]}},"person_4195610_translations":{"at":1773060336718,"data":{"id":4195610,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Benjamin Cléry","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"FR","iso_639_1":"fr","name":"Français","english_name":"French","data":{"biography":"Benjamin Cléry est un acteur français né le 28 octobre 1997. Après avoir débuté le théâtre au lycée, il intègre le Cours Florent en 2015. Il participe ensuite à de nombreux projets pour la télévision comme pour le cinéma.","name":"Benjamin Cléry","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Бенджамин Клери","primary":false}}]}},"person_240273_translations":{"at":1773319434957,"data":{"id":240273,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Andrea Sartoretti","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"IT","iso_639_1":"it","name":"Italiano","english_name":"Italian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Andrea Sartoretti","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Андреа Сарторетти","primary":false}}]}},"person_584971_translations":{"at":1773319435884,"data":{"id":584971,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Stefan Valdobrev is a Bulgarian actor, film composer, writer and singer-songwriter.","name":"Stefan Valdobrev","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"BG","iso_639_1":"bg","name":"български език","english_name":"Bulgarian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Stefan Valdobrev","primary":true}}]}},"movie_1339618_keywords":{"at":1773319436308,"data":{"id":1339618,"keywords":[]}}}}